RE-SET @ Bridge__48 | Moonamour x Bejaus 01.06 | Barcelona

*RE-SET*
Hailing from the southwest of Germany, RE-SET has been producing raw/hypnotic techno for over 8 years. RE-SET has graced stages across Germany, including a residency at the renowned U60311 event series with his Friend:Holger Heber as Duo in Frankfurt am Main, he also played in famous Clubs like Silodom/Saarbr√ºcken, Elektrok√ºche ect. Before moving to Barcelona two years ago, he has focused on his solo project, releasing music on esteemed labels like R3VOLUTION, CombineAudio, STRGHTX and Jeton. In Barcelona, RE-SET has already brought his unique sound to clubs like Jaggys and Bejause Cafe, and is set to electrify the city's nightlife with upcoming gigs. As a producer and DJ, RE-SET continues to push the boundaries of techno, delivering high-energy performances and innovative tracks that leave a lasting impression. Occasionally, he also enjoys mixing it up with special house sets, taking inspiration from the early 2010s, showcasing his versatility and eclectic taste. Stay tuned for more.
